What you need to know:

Those backing Mr Mvurya, and by extension Dr Ruto, have revealed plans to form their own party, further escalating the onslaught to dethrone Mr Joho and depose ODM from the helm of Coast politics.Last week, Mr Joho toured Garsen in Tana River County to drum up support for Building Bridges Initiative (BBI) and declared his intention to contest for the presidency.